9 An Act relating to cities and towns; amending 11 O.S.
2021, Section 14-106, which relates to the
10 requirement of publication of municipal ordinances;
modifying requirement to publish ordinance to thirty
11 days after passage; and providing an effective date.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 11 O.S. 2021, Section 14-106, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 14-106. No ordinance having any subject other than the
18 appropriation of monies shall be in force unless published or posted
19 within fifteen (15) thirty (30) days after its passage. Every
20 municipal ordinance shall be published at least once in full, except
21 as provided for in Section 14-107 of this title. When publishing
22 the ordinance, the publisher or managing officer of the newspaper
23 shall prefix to the ordinance a line in brackets stating the date of
24
